to offer you some advice.

16:26.678 --> 16:29.745
You know, I'd encourage
you to count your blessings.

16:30.257 --> 16:32.228
You're married to an incredible woman,

16:32.442 --> 16:34.253
and you've got a second incredible woman

16:34.278 --> 16:36.055
