17:21.598 --> 17:22.832
And for what?

17:23.435 --> 17:25.635
You know, some Hail Mary
chance at having a baby?

17:25.670 --> 17:27.670
It's just... it's just not worth it.

17:27.704 --> 17:30.566
So I think it's time that
we just both take a step back

17:30.584 --> 17:31.709
