18:13.626 --> 18:15.435
Yeah, you thought you
did, and then I went nuts.

18:15.459 --> 18:17.418
You did. You definitely did.

18:18.698 --> 18:21.148
But I know who you are.

18:21.434 --> 18:23.734
You're a kind and wonderful man

18:23.770 --> 18:26.604
